# 💰 Loan Approval Prediction using Machine Learning

## 📌 Overview
This project predicts whether a loan application will be approved or not using machine learning techniques. The system analyzes applicant details such as income, credit history, loan amount, and other relevant factors to make predictions.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Data preprocessing and cleaning  
- Handling missing values  
- Feature encoding  
- Model training and prediction  
- Model evaluation  
- Loan approval status prediction  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python  
- Pandas  
- NumPy  
- Matplotlib  
- Scikit-learn  

---

## 📊 Workflow
1. Data Collection  
2. Data Preprocessing  
3. Feature Engineering  
4. Model Training  
5. Model Evaluation  
6. Prediction  

---

## 📈 Results
The system predicts loan approval based on applicant details with good accuracy. Performance is evaluated using standard evaluation metrics.

